            <thetext>With the 2.34.0 release, the triggerEvent method was removed from the Selenium Core JS API:

https://code.google.com/p/selenium/source/browse/java/CHANGELOG?name=2.34.0

We use this method in the qx user extensions for Selenium to focus a DOM element before simulating a click, so qxClick and similar methods throw an exception. We should replace this call with doFocus.</thetext>
